9.  Under the supervision of the team leader, the study team will 

(i)  prepare literature and policy reviews and research outlines before the inception 
workshop; 
(ii)  participate and present in the inception workshop, and revise the literature and 
policy  reviews  and  research  outlines  based  on  comments  received  from 
discussants and workshop participants; 
(iii)  prepare  draft  background  research  papers  according  to  the  agreed  outlines 
before the finalization workshop; 
(iv)  participate and present in the finalization workshop, and revise the background 
research papers based on comments received from discussants and workshop 
participants;  
(v)  finalize the background research papers; and 
(vi)  contribute to the synthesis report and book publication, as needed.
